Shadow (32) <br>
The Witch King, Lord of the Nazgul x 3 <br>
Ulaire Enquea, Ringwraith in Twilight x 2 <br>
Ulaire Attea, The Easterling x 2 <br>
Ulaire Nelya, Ringwraith in Twilight x 2 <br>
Bill Ferny, Swarthy, Sneering, Fellow <br>
Ulaire Otsea, Liutenant of Morgul x 2 <br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(146)">Morgul Skulker</a> x 3 <br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(984)">Resistance Becomes Unbearable</a> x 4 <br>
